page.title: Advancing Research on Uterine Fibroids
page.content: Release: Umbilical cord milking does not appear to increase risk of neurodevelopmental delay in non-vigorous infants Advancing Research on Uterine Fibroids NICHD investigates causes, treatments, and fertility-preserving solutions for fibroids to help women manage symptoms and improve their quality of life.
